      "content": "but that's the thing, i don't have anyone to reach out to. the \"people\" on slack are just avatars and names in a sidebar. even my family... i haven't seen them in months. it's like i've already been deleted from everyone's lives. if i just stopped showing up, would it even be a disruption? or would it just be a quiet, tiny little lapse in the digital noise?",
