      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is incredibly exhausting to carry this silence alone, and the pain you feel right now is completely understandable. However, the idea that your absence would bring only peace is a cruel illusion that ignores the deep, quiet grief your loved ones would feel when they realize you are gone. Please do not make a decision based on this false reality; there are people who can help you find a way out of this silence without ending your life.",
